  "description": {
    "zh": "你在森林里活动了这么多次，应该注意到那里有多少渣滓在游荡了吧？\n\n美军、湖边的Boss、邪教徒……这些都只是冰山一角。实际上，森林里到处都是Scav和PMC，简直让人难以置信。\n\n准备好开始清理了吗？把那些家伙全都解决掉，顺便干掉一些伐木场的地头蛇小弟们和三狗小队。任务可不轻松，但对你来说应该没问题吧？",
    "en": "So you've been in the local forest a lot of times already, did you ever notice how much scum wanders around there?\nImports, a gang at the lake, and cultists, and those are just the ones who are worth mentioning, there are a ton of bandits and operators aswell. You'd think that there aren't many people in that place, but that isn't the case, weird.\n\nAnyway, ready to clean it up a little? Get rid of each and everyone of them, and take down a bunch of operators and bandits while you're at it, and don't forget the bodyguards of the gang leader, the imports also walk around as a trio."
  },
